{"tid":383901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲死臭雞成日都有仔纏住？？？","createTime":"2017-09-02T00:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T01:10:40.000Z","uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1508c3d5743da6a2269b4fab0139cecca7c4eb8","tid":383901,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:07:05.000Z","msg":"點解啲俾人屌到鬆晒嘅臭閪成日會有咁多男人纏，啲男人係咪鍾意食二手嘢，去m記都食啲食剩嘅薯條，有錢都唔買餐，剩係鍾意食二手閪。俾人屌到臭晒都仲有咁多男人鍾意，係咪男人剩係對住陣閪臭味先起到機。係咪有啲臭閪團係我唔知，啲男人一齊組團纏住啲臭閪。啲死臭雞又臭串有啲仲要唔係靚，但係都仲有咁多男人纏，真係好難明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係咪有男人專食二手臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"8420afecaac378cd8fe0a0344822b089eef71e1e","tid":383901,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"任嗌㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e8bd80d436b5672d266064bbaa7bda76b3b362","tid":383901,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>任嗌㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊做兵呀頂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4f176ab78210d3fb70012a01e3a811657f25b3","tid":383901,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"又唔係做人世<br />\neasy come easy go"},{"pid":"65464295ad0a5694466bf3acb5ce42b6ed4fd9df","tid":383901,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:25:34.000Z","msg":"鹹香嘢特別多烏蠅嬲"},{"pid":"27e4c42378a6d261e1827118895aa70848b8550b","tid":383901,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鹹香嘢特別多烏蠅嬲</blockquote><br />\n真，啲垃圾牛肺特別多人嬲，但係一品鮑就無人嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/n